## First Heading (H2)

Write your intro paragraph here. The first H2 should hook the reader and set up the rest of the post.

You can use **bold text** for emphasis, *italic for subtle emphasis*, and [links to other pages](https://example.com).

## Second Heading

More content here. You can include:

- Bullet point one
- Bullet point two
- Bullet point three

### Subheading (H3)

You can use H3 for subsections under H2.

![Alt text for image](https://framerusercontent.com/images/YOUR_INLINE_IMAGE.png)

## Another Section

Just keep writing with H2 headers for each major section. The template will handle the styling automatically.

## Conclusion

End with a strong conclusion that ties everything back to Great Marketing AI.

---

## How to use this template

1. Copy this file and rename it to your-blog-slug.mdx (no spaces, all lowercase, use hyphens)
2. Fill out the frontmatter at the top (between the --- lines)
3. Write your content in Markdown below the frontmatter
4. Upload to GitHub at content/blog/your-blog-slug.mdx
5. Vercel auto-deploys
6. Your blog goes live at greatmarketing.ai/blog/your-blog-slug

NOTES:
- The slug = the filename (without .mdx). So "how-to-rank.mdx" becomes greatmarketing.ai/blog/how-to-rank
- Read time is auto-calculated from your content
- Keep keyTakeaways and faqs short (3-5 items each is ideal)
- Use ## for main sections (H2), ### for sub-sections (H3)
- Bold = **text**, Italic = *text*, Links = [text](url)
